{"tid":1957172,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"其實解決偽黃餐廳嘅問題好簡單","createTime":"2020-04-03T16:51:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-03T16:53:55.000Z","uid":201837,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"7594baf9b64cea9b08fd02d9b1e9eebb9e96e10d","tid":1957172,"uid":201837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T16:51:55.000Z","msg":"懶人包：平時食多幾間，唔好淨係食死一間<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">以下係for個人方面，如果講緊係捐錢個啲，唔該你fc清楚先好捐。</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔好get錯，我唔係話fc唔重要<br />\n<br />\n呢排好多所謂&ldquo;呃錢&rdquo;嘅事件無啦啦一單接一單爆出黎，老實講我個人就覺得諗黎都無謂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔通你要每一間都好似CIA咁起哂所有野出黎咩?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就算起完都係得少部分人會真係會去分析會去睇，大部分都係見人傳咩就傳。好容易傳錯。<br />\n<br />\n其實好多時有啲野根本fc唔到，佢話告急唔通你又知佢每日營業額幾多咩，大家都係講個「信」字。你有能力咪去幫手買吓嘢囉。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">所以，我嘅諗法係分散投資<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔好淨係食出名個啲</span></span><br />\n好多時會見到淨係得出名嘅有人排，結果周圍幾間都冇人，e.g.黃埔龍門<span style=\"font-size: small;\">btw咖哩厚豬好撚正</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n宜家大把黃店list，就算係位置比較偏啲嘅你都會知，唔洗你慢慢行哂成個區去搵，所以<span style=\"color: red;\">由今日起，每個人去down自己個區嘅list，跟住個順序食，仲幫埋你諗每日食咩，另外可以最少一個禮拜幫襯一次告急，成個區每人一次點都夠啦掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"880a956090fb1fa5ab4072961f82f9e370dd0d9a","tid":1957172,"uid":201837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T16:53:44.000Z","msg":"熊茶呢啲叫埋狗就知咩事啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" 